5 years of relevant experience;
Diploma of professional studies in a related field;
Sense of analysis and attention to detail;
Good organizational capacity;
Good knowledge of Excel;
Good communication skills (customer service);
Dynamism and great flexibility in performing tasks in a dynamic environment;
